title: UFC : events with the highest live attendance as of May 2019
summary: This bar chart has 18 columns on the x axis representing Ufc Fights, and Attendance in each Ufc Fights on the y axis.
Ufc Fights Rousey vs Holm (UFC 193) has the highest Attendance and Miocic vs Overeem (UFC 203) has the lowest Attendance.
The Attendance of Ufc Fights Miocic vs Overeem (UFC 203) is 2.99% smaller than the maximum value at Rousey vs Holm (UFC 193).
